SELECT
	"RequisitionHistory"."Requisition_ID" AS "Requisition",
	'CreateRequisition_' || "RequisitionHistory"."ID" AS "ID",
	"RequisitionHistory"."CreateDate" AS "Time"
FROM "o_custom_RequisitionHistory" AS "RequisitionHistory"
JOIN "o_custom_Requisition" AS "Requisition" ON 1=1
  AND "RequisitionHistory"."Requisition_ID" = "Requisition"."ID"
WHERE 1=1
    AND "RequisitionHistory"."CreateDate" IS NOT NULL
    AND "RequisitionHistory"."VersionNumber" = 1

sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT
	'CreateRequisition_' || "RequisitionHistory"."ID" AS "ID",
	"RequisitionItem"."ContractItem_ID" AS "ContractItem"
FROM "o_custom_RequisitionHistory" AS "RequisitionHistory"
JOIN "o_custom_Requisition" AS "Requisition" ON 1=1
  AND "RequisitionHistory"."Requisition_ID" = "Requisition"."ID"
JOIN "o_custom_RequisitionItem" AS "RequisitionItem" ON 1=1
    AND "Requisition"."ID" = "RequisitionItem"."Requisition_ID"
WHERE 1=1
    AND "RequisitionItem"."ContractItem_ID" IS NOT NULL
    AND "RequisitionHistory"."CreateDate" IS NOT NULL
    AND "RequisitionHistory"."VersionNumber" = 1

SELECT
	'CreateRequisition_' || "RequisitionHistory"."ID" AS "ID",
	"OperationalContract"."ID" AS "OperationalContract"
FROM "o_custom_RequisitionHistory" AS "RequisitionHistory"
JOIN "o_custom_Requisition" AS "Requisition" ON 1=1
  AND "RequisitionHistory"."Requisition_ID" = "Requisition"."ID"
JOIN "o_custom_RequisitionItem" AS "Item" ON 1=1
    AND "Requisition"."ID" =  "Item"."Requisition_ID"
JOIN "o_custom_OperationalContract" AS "OperationalContract" ON 1=1
    AND "Item"."OperationalContract_ID" =  "OperationalContract"."ID"
WHERE 1=1
    AND "OperationalContract"."ID" IS NOT NULL
    AND "RequisitionHistory"."CreateDate" IS NOT NULL
    AND "RequisitionHistory"."VersionNumber" = 1

SELECT
	'CreateRequisition_' || "RequisitionHistory"."ID" AS "ID",
    "RequisitionItem"."PurchaseRequisitionItem_ID" AS "PurchaseRequisitionItem"
FROM "o_custom_RequisitionHistory" AS "RequisitionHistory"
JOIN "o_custom_Requisition" AS "Requisition" ON 1=1
  AND "RequisitionHistory"."Requisition_ID" = "Requisition"."ID"
JOIN "o_custom_RequisitionItem" AS "RequisitionItem" ON 1=1
    AND "Requisition"."ID" = "RequisitionItem"."Requisition_ID"
WHERE 1=1
    AND "RequisitionItem"."PurchaseRequisitionItem_ID" IS NOT NULL
    AND "RequisitionHistory"."CreateDate" IS NOT NULL
    AND "RequisitionHistory"."VersionNumber" = 1

SELECT
	'CreateRequisition_' || "RequisitionHistory"."ID" AS "ID",
	"Item"."ID" AS "RequisitionItem"
FROM "o_custom_RequisitionHistory" AS "RequisitionHistory"
JOIN "o_custom_Requisition" AS "Requisition" ON 1=1
  AND "RequisitionHistory"."Requisition_ID" = "Requisition"."ID"
JOIN "o_custom_RequisitionItem" AS "Item" ON 1=1
    AND "Requisition"."ID" =  "Item"."Requisition_ID"
WHERE 1=1
    AND "Item"."ID" IS NOT NULL
    AND "RequisitionHistory"."CreateDate" IS NOT NULL
    AND "RequisitionHistory"."VersionNumber" = 1
